# MetaMask Design System - Components

This document lists all available components in the MetaMask Design System. Import them from `@/lib/components`.

## Component Architecture

```
1. TOKENS (from ./tokens.ts)
   └── colors, typography, spacing, radius, shadow
   └── Single source of truth for all design values

2. BASE COMPONENTS (primitives)
   └── Button, Input, Card, Badge, Avatar, Switch, etc.
   └── Building blocks - use tokens directly

3. COMPLEX COMPONENTS (composed from base)
   └── HubHeader, TokenCell, TokenList, AccountPicker, etc.
   └── Compose base components + add layout/business logic

4. SCREENS (composed from complex components)
   └── WalletHome, Settings, Send, Receive, etc.
```

